description:
Join us for a comprehensive and enlightening session at Atta Galatta, with author Aishwarya Jha and executive editor, Penguin Random House India, Venkatesh Karthik, as they take us over the secrets behind writing and publishing a successful debut novel. This session will cover:

Turning the seed of an idea into a script;
Bringing characters to life;
The importance of setting;
The querying process;
What editors are looking for: and
Troubleshooting & common pitfalls.
